parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to lock or become difficult to turn, leading to loss of control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels hard or difficult to turn
the steering wheel locks or seizes
the vehicle is hard to maneuver
especially at low speeds
and there may be a loud noise or vibration when turning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause the steering wheel to lock or become difficult to turn, leading to loss of control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels hard or difficult to turn
the steering wheel locks or seizes
the vehicle is hard to maneuver
especially at low speeds
and there may be a loud noise or vibration when turning.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electronic Stability Control and ABS Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic stability control and ABS systems can cause the vehicle to lose traction and stability, leading to loss of control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The electronic stability control and ABS lights illuminate on the dashboard
the vehicle is difficult to control
especially on slippery or uneven surfaces
and there may be a loss of traction or stability.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Tank and Fuel Line Leaks
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Fuel leaks can cause a fire hazard, potentially leading to serious accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Strong fuel smell
fuel leaking from the top of the fuel tank
fuel puddles on the ground
fuel fumes in the cabin
difficulty starting the engine
check engine light on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the non-deployment of airbags in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injury or fatality to the occupants.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the passenger airbag light stays off
the "Service Air Bag" message appears on the dashboard
the airbag does not deploy in an accident
the passenger seat does not register occupancy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger presence module can cause the passenger airbag to malfunction, leading to the non-deployment of the airbag in an accident, increasing the risk of injury or fatality to the passenger.
symptoms: The passenger airbag light stays off
the passenger seat does not register occupancy
the airbag does not deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the non-deployment of airbags in an accident, increasing the risk of injury or fatality to the occupants.
symptoms: The "Service Air Bag" message appears on the dashboard
the airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag does not deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Pump Failure and Fuel Leaks
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump and fuel leaks can cause a fire hazard, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Strong smell of gasoline inside and outside the vehicle
fuel leaks
fuel dripping onto the ground
fuel pump failure
cracked fuel pump module
fuel tank cracks
and engine stalling or difficulty starting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch pedal can cause difficulty shifting gears, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
clutch pedal sticks to the floor
clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
and the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Key remains stuck in the ignition switch
airbag warning light illuminates
and difficulty starting the vehicle.
